{"tid":1192281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣氣象學家被取消聯合國會議資格","createTime":"2019-06-08T10:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T11:00:13.000Z","uid":37554,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c29e86308c64a1ac05a4c2022994b01140863d67","tid":1192281,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:42:24.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】台灣一名氣象學家應邀以觀察員身分出席聯合國世界氣象大會，期間突然被取消資格。<br />\n<br />\n在瑞士日內瓦舉行的世界氣象大會為期約兩周，台灣民營企業「天氣風險公司」總經理彭啟明早前收到大會邀請函後，報名參加其中三天會議，他說周三順利出席，但周四進場後不久警衛請他去秘書處，秘書處人員說會議只有聯合國成員國代表才能出席，他沒有資格參加，並且強行取走掛在他脖子上的名牌，彭啟明當時詢問是否與大陸有關，秘書處人員回答說「不能說」。<br />\n<br />\n每四年舉行一次的世界氣象大會是聯合國世界氣象組織會議，自1971年退出聯合國後台灣一直未能再參加，彭啟明說出席會議期間注意到大陸代表一直盯着他，沒想到此行不是代表台灣當局，也沒有當局支持經費都會受到政治打壓。"},{"pid":"2b472ea7f4021108677357c4eee488c7bc48fa34","tid":1192281,"uid":4783,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"聯合國真係垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持美國唔撚交會費由佢收皮"},{"pid":"01e3a4c34b117fc64ce5adade1c0d564d14bf9d5","tid":1192281,"uid":41500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:49:46.000Z","msg":"唔駛問又係口講非政治化,做就最政治化個共支搞事啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d3367375076eb7f903b536d040d39fc239a041","tid":1192281,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52136bd0c5cf79fa07a526ae87204c2d758dafaa","tid":1192281,"uid":62506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:58:58.000Z","msg":"國際組織得淡笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得會委任禿鷹，物以類聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6ca942f97ff0b723927a1c17e50d546986bee3","tid":1192281,"uid":2654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:00:13.000Z","msg":"UN幾點收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}